physical_examinations.relevant_findings: Denies fever, new vision changes, earaches, change in hearing, sore throat, palpitations, leg swelling, cough, shortness of breath, wheezing, hemoptysis, new joint pain, swelling or muscle weakness, depression, hallucinations, suicidal thoughts, bleeding, skin changes, rashes or lesions, dizziness, headache, syncope, seizures, vomiting, melena, hematemesis, difficulty urinating, hematuria, changes in appetite, cold or heat intolerance, increased thirst.
